00:41:53,250 --> 00:41:54,180
of his own pride,

873
00:41:54,370 --> 00:41:55,100
he once again

874
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:56,850
kicked all of this city's money

875
00:41:56,850 --> 00:41:58,250
straight into the river,

876
00:41:58,270 --> 00:42:00,530
not caring if it'd flood the whole place!

877
00:42:14,890 --> 00:42:15,850
Okay, okay.

878
00:42:16,210 --> 00:42:17,160
I understand.

879
00:42:21,690 --> 00:42:22,520
Baoquan,

880
00:42:22,780 --> 00:42:24,180
Mr. Yu just called.

881
00:42:24,210 --> 00:42:25,730
He wants you
to go to the Ningbo Chamber of Commerce

882
00:42:25,730 --> 00:42:26,480
to discuss

883
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,870
the disbandment of the merchant militia.

884
00:42:27,870 --> 00:42:28,790
Disbandment?

885
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:30,580
Whose idea is that?

886
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:32,640
H-How would I know?

887
00:42:33,120 --> 00:42:34,480
Mr. Yu said on the phone

888
00:42:35,850 --> 00:42:37,730
that the circuit intendant
of Shanghai has resigned.

889
00:42:37,730 --> 00:42:38,810
Technically,

890
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,000
he should be

891
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:41,930
in charge of the merchant militia.

892
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:44,000
That's what he said.

893
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,460
Don't ask me to explain it.

894
00:42:46,730 --> 00:42:49,080
Mr. Yu has lost his mind.

895
00:42:50,850 --> 00:42:52,000
We poured a fortune

896
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,000
into building that armed force.

897
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,440
How can we just hand it over?

898
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:55,440
Who knows when

899
00:42:55,730 --> 00:42:58,040
we might need
to change our way of speaking?

900
00:42:58,040 --> 00:42:58,600
Go, go, go.

901
00:42:58,600 --> 00:42:59,300
Call for a car.

902
00:42:59,300 --> 00:43:00,480
I'm going to
the Ningbo Chamber of Commerce.

903
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:01,010
Okay.
